#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kooka; is a &kde; application that provides access to scanner hardware "
#| "using the <ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/\">SANE</ulink> "
#| "library. Therefore, the <acronym>SANE</acronym> package must be installed "
#| "to use &kooka;."
msgid ""
"&kooka; is an application that provides access to scanner hardware using the "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/\">SANE</ulink> library. Therefore, "
"the <acronym>SANE</acronym> package must be installed to use &kooka;."
msgstr ""
"&kooka; on &kde; rakendus, mis võimaldab hõlpsasti skannida <acronym>SANE</"
"acronym> teeke kasutades. Seepärast peab pakett <acronym>SANE</acronym> "
"olema paigaldatud, muidu &kooka; kasutamine ei õnnestu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kooka; allows you to scan, save and view in any image format that &kde; "
#| "supports."
msgid ""
"&kooka; allows you to scan, save and view in any image format that &Qt; "
"supports."
msgstr ""
"&kooka; võimaldab skannida, salvestada ja vaadata kõiki pildivorminguid, "
"mida &kde; toetab."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Character recognition is also provided by using the open source <ulink "
#| "url=\"http://jocr.sourceforge.net/\">GOCR</ulink> or <ulink url=\"http://"
#| "www.gnu.org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html\">OCRAD</ulink> programs, or the "
#| "commercial <ulink url=\"http://www.rerecognition.com/\">KADMOS</ulink> "
#| "library. You have to install at least one of these software packages to "
#| "use this functionality. After character recognition is complete, a "
#| "spellcheck is automatically started for the recognized material. You can "
#| "edit the content in the <guilabel>OCR</guilabel> window and export it as "
#| "plain text."
msgid ""
"Character recognition is also provided by using the open source <ulink url="
"\"http://jocr.sourceforge.net/\">GOCR</ulink> or <ulink url=\"http://www.gnu."
"org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html\">OCRAD</ulink> programs, or the commercial "
"<ulink url=\"https://rerecognition.com/en/products/kadmos-icr-ocr/\">KADMOS</"
"ulink> library. You have to install at least one of these software packages "
"to use this functionality. After character recognition is complete, a "
"spellcheck is automatically started for the recognized material. You can "
"edit the content in the <guilabel>OCR</guilabel> window and export it as "
"plain text."
msgstr ""
"Samuti on võimalik optiline märgituvastus kas avatud lähtekoodiga "
"programmide <ulink url=\"http://jocr.sourceforge.net/\">GOCR</ulink> ja "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.gnu.org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html\">OCRAD</ulink> "
"või kommertstarkvara <ulink url=\"http://www.rerecognition.com/\">KADMOS</"
"ulink> teegi abil. Selleks tuleb paigaldada vähemalt üks mainitud "
"tarkvarapakettidest. Kui märgituvastus on tehtud, käivitatakse äratuntud "
"osal automaatselt õigekirja kontroll. Sisu saab muuta <guilabel>OMT</"
"guilabel> aknas ning selle siis eksportida lihttekstina."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Instructions"
msgstr "Juhtnöörid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The web site <ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/\">http://www.sane-"
"project.org</ulink> has information about supported scanners. Refer to it "
"before purchasing a scanner, if possible."
msgstr ""
"Infot toetatud skannerite kohta saav veebileheküljelt <ulink url=\"http://"
"www.mostang.com/sane\">http://www.sane-project.org</ulink>. Kui võimalik, "
"uurige sobivust enne skanneri ostmist."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The &kooka; Main Window</title>"
msgstr "<title>&kooka; põhiaken</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The &kooka; Main Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kooka; põhiaken</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Start &kooka; from a console by simply entering "
#| "<userinput><command>kooka</command></userinput> or select it from the "
#| "<guilabel>Graphics</guilabel> submenu in the application starter. Create "
#| "a link on the &kde; desktop, which uses a scanner icon, if desired."
msgid ""
"Start &kooka; from a console by simply entering <userinput><command>kooka</"
"command></userinput> or select it from the <guilabel>Graphics</guilabel> "
"submenu in the application starter. Create a link on the desktop, which uses "
"a scanner icon, if desired."
msgstr ""
"&kooka; saab käivitada käsurealt korraldusega <userinput><command>kooka</"
"command></userinput> või valides selle rakenduse käivitusmenüü alammenüüst "
"<guilabel>Graafika</guilabel>. Soovi korral võid luua &kde; töölauale "
"skanneri ikooniga viida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use &kooka; only for optical character recognition without connecting to "
"a scanner start the application in gallery mode with "
"<userinput><command>kooka</command> <option>-g</option></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"&kooka; kasutamiseks ainult optilise märgituvastuse huvides ilma skanneriga "
"ühendumata käivita rakendus galeriirežiimis käsuga "
"<userinput><command>kooka</command> <option>-g</option></userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main window in &kooka; consists of three frames. At the top, see both "
"icon and a menu panels. Use the mouse to enlarge or reduce the windows as "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"&kooka; põhiaken koosneb kolmest osast. Ülal asuvad nii ikooni- kui "
"menüüriba. Osade suurendamiseks või kahandamiseks saab kasutada hiirt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The navigation window consists of three tabs, which allow you to switch "
#| "between the <guilabel>Scan</guilabel>, <guilabel>OCR</guilabel> and the "
#| "integrated file browser called the <guilabel>Gallery</guilabel>. The "
#| "working folder is displayed in the lower part of the window along with "
#| "the folder where the scan will be saved."
msgid ""
"The navigation window consists of three tabs, which allow you to switch "
"between the <guilabel>Scan</guilabel>, <guilabel>OCR</guilabel> and the "
"integrated file browser called the <guilabel>Gallery</guilabel>. The working "
"folder is displayed in the upper part of the window along with the folder "
"where the scan will be saved."
msgstr ""
"Liikumisaken koosneb kolmest kaardist, mis võimaldavad valida kas "
"<guilabel>skannimise</guilabel>e, <guilabel>OMT</guilabel> või integreeritud "
"faililehitseja ehk <guilabel>galerii</guilabel>. Töökataloogi näidatakse "
"akna alumises osas kõrvuti kataloogiga, kuhu skannimise tulemus salvestada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make your scanner-dependent settings, which are dependent on the scanner you "
"have connected, in the lower left window. Usually, these are settings for "
"resolution, brightness and contrast, scanning mode (&eg;, color, gray, or "
"binary), and for gamma values."
msgstr ""
"Akna alumises vasakus osas saab seadistada skanneripõhiseid asju, tavaliselt "
"on neiks resolutsioon, heledus, kontrast, skannimisrežiim (&eg; värviline, "
"halltoonides või binaarne) ning gammaväärtused."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure your settings here first. Afterwards, initiate the preview scan "
"with <guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem>. The scan result will then appear in "
"the right pane."
msgstr ""
"Määra kõigepealt vajalikud seadistused. Seejärel käivita eelvaatlus "
"menüükäsuga <guimenuitem>Eelvaatlus</guimenuitem>.  Skannimise tulemus ilmub "
"nähtavale parempoolsel paneelil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the area to scan in the preview image itself with the mouse to define "
"the final dimensions."
msgstr ""
"Lõplike mõõtmete määramiseks vali skannitav ala hiirega eelvaatluse pildil "
"endal."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After this is done, click <guimenu>Scan</guimenu> to scan the selection made "
"in the preview. After scanning, you will be asked in which format to save "
"the image whether to make this your standard format (without being prompted "
"to confirm your selection in the future)."
msgstr ""
"Kui see on tehtud, klõpsa käsule <guimenu>Skanni</guimenu>, et skannida "
"eelvaatluses määratud valik. Skannimise järel küsitakse sinu käest, millises "
"vormingus kujutis salvestada ja kas muuta see standardvorminguks (mis "
"tähendab, et edaspidi selle vormingu puhul enam kinnitust ei küsita)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you checked that you do not want to be asked about the save format, the "
"memory assistant will no longer appear. To change the format some time in "
"the future, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Kooka...</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Image Saving</"
"guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Always use the Save Assistant</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Kui märgid, et ei soovi enam näha küsimust salvestamise vormingu kohta, ei "
"näegi sa enam salvestusabilist. Kui soovid kunagi siiski vormingut muuta, "
"saad seda teha menüükäsuga <menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Kooka seadistamine...</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Pildi "
"salvestamine</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Alati kasutatakse salvestusabilist</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "The large window shows how the image appears after a final scan."
msgstr ""
"Suur aken näitab, milline näeb kujutis välja pärast lõplikku skannimist."

